# 06/25/25   KA      Audio pd support is added
# 05/30/25   KA      Clients per pd and i3c instance increased for target specific
# 03/17/25   SS      SWA for Kaanapali QUP AXI HW Bug
# 03/04/25   AY      Added support for BT PD
# 07/29/24   GKR     Added a FEATURE FLAG to specific to ADSP PROC code
# 07/14/24   GKR     Added Dynamic Chipset folder check for stub decision making
# 07/12/24   GKR     Stubbed out QUP COMMON for PW enablement
# 06/26/24   GKR     FEATURE Flag for SDC PROC Support
# 06/05/24   KSN     Added changes for pd agnostic fr
# 10/31/23   KGA     Added changes to make MAX_IBI_INSTANCE and MAX_I3C_INSTANCE Macro to target specific.
# 07/30/23   bng     Added Flag to support transfer optimization in island
# 06/20/23   GKR     Added KPI Profiling SUPPORT based on FLAG
